casebody.data:
FIRST NATIONAL BANK OF BRADENTON v. CITY OF BRADEN-TON, et al. 18 So. (2nd) 166

January Term, 1944

May 26, 1944 En Banc W. L. Kimball and E. Calvin Johnson, for appellant. Hubert Blakey, for appellees. PER CURIAM:

The Court having duly considered the appeal and cross appeal and no error appearing in the decree the same is affirmed.

BUFORD, C. J., TERRELL, BROWN, THOMAS, ADAMS and SEBRING, JJ., concur. CHAPMAN, J., dissents.
